trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.ComponentsCreated" /> event that occurs when components are added to the toolbox.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona datos para el evento <see cref="E:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.ComponentsCreated" /> que se produce cuando se agregan componentes al cuadro de herramientas.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.ComponentsCreated> event is raised when components are added to the toolbox.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.ComponentsCreated> evento se desencadena cuando se agregan componentes al cuadro de herramientas.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxComponentsCreatedEventArgs> provides data indicating which component or components are being added.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxComponentsCreatedEventArgs> Proporciona datos que indican qué componente o los componentes se van a agregar.

trans-unit.source: The following example method returns a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxComponentsCreatedEventArgs> that indicates the components that have been created:
trans-unit.target: El siguiente método de ejemplo devuelve un <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxComponentsCreatedEventArgs> que indica los componentes que se han creado:

trans-unit.source: The components to include in the toolbox.
trans-unit.target: Componentes que se van a incluir en el cuadro de herramientas.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxComponentsCreatedEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxComponentsCreatedEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an array containing the components to add to the toolbox.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece una matriz que contiene los componentes que se van a agregar al cuadro de herramientas.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> indicating the components to add to the toolbox.
trans-unit.target: Una matriz de tipo <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> que indica los componentes que se van a agregar al cuadro de herramientas.
